{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"matrix()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transform-function/matrix","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>CSS 函数 <code>matrix()</code> 指定了一个由指定的 6 个值组成的 2D 变换矩阵。这种矩阵的常量值是隐含的，而不是由参数传递的；其他的参数是以列优先的顺序描述的。</p>\n\n<p><code>matrix(a, b, c, d, tx, ty)</code> 是 <code>matrix3d(a, b, 0, 0, c, d, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, tx, ty, 0, 1)</code> 的简写。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\"><strong>注意：</strong> 直到 Firefox 16, Gecko 才接受对于 <strong>tx</strong> 和<strong> ty </strong>的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/length\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a> 值。</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">matrix(<em>a</em>, <em>b</em>, <em>c</em>, <em>d</em>, <em>tx</em>, <em>ty</em>)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数值","title":"参数值","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"a\"><em>a</em> <em>b</em> <em>c</em> <em>d</em></dt>\n <dd>描述线性变换的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/number\"><code>&lt;number&gt;</code></a> 。</dd>\n <dt id=\"tx\"><em>tx</em> <em>ty</em></dt>\n <dd>描述如何应用这个变换的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/number\"><code>&lt;number&gt;</code></a> 。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">ℝ<sup>2 </sup>下的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%AC%9B%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%94%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E7%B3%BB\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">笛卡尔坐标</a></th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">ℝℙ<sup>2&nbsp; </sup>下<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BD%90%E6%AC%A1%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">齐次坐标</a></th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">ℝ<sup>3</sup>下的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%AC%9B%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%94%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E7%B3%BB\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">笛卡尔坐标</a></th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">ℝℙ<sup>3</sup>下的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BD%90%E6%AC%A1%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">齐次坐标</a></th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><math> <mfenced> <mtable> <mtr><mtd>a</mtd><mtd>c</mtd></mtr> <mtr><mtd>b</mtd><mtd>d</mtd></mtr> </mtable> </mfenced> </math></td>\n   <td>\n    <p><math> <mfenced> <mtable> <mtr><mtd></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math><br>\n     a&nbsp;&nbsp;c&nbsp;&nbsp;tx<br>\n     b&nbsp;&nbsp;d&nbsp;&nbsp;ty<br>\n     0&nbsp; 0&nbsp;&nbsp;1</p>\n   </td>\n   <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><math> <mfenced> <mtable> <mtr><mtd></mtd></mtr>a&nbsp; c&nbsp; tx</mtable></mfenced></math><br>\n    b&nbsp; d&nbsp; ty<br>\n    0&nbsp; 0&nbsp; 1<mtr><mtd></mtd></mtr>  </td>\n   <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><math> <mfenced> <mtable> <mtr><mtd>a</mtd><mtd>c</mtd><mtd>0</mtd><mtd>tx</mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd>b</mtd><mtd>d</mtd><mtd>0</mtd><mtd>ty</mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd>0</mtd><mtd>0</mtd><mtd>1</mtd><mtd>0</mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd>0</mtd><mtd>0</mtd><mtd>0</mtd><mtd>1</mtd></mtr></mtable> </mfenced> </math></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>[a b c d tx ty]</code></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>这些值表示以下函数：</p>\n\n<p>matrix( scaleX(), skewY(), skewX(), scaleY(), translateX(), translateY() )</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;div&gt;Normal&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\"changed\"&gt;Changed&lt;/div&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">div {\n  width: 80px;\n  height: 80px;\n  background-color: skyblue;\n}\n\n.changed {\n  transform: matrix(1, 2, -1, 1, 80, 80);\n  background-color: pink;\n}\n\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"结果","title":"结果","isH3":true,"content":"<p>请看英文版案例&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transform-function/matrix#Result\" aria-current=\"page\">/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transform-function/matrix#Result</a></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"参数值","id":"参数值"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"}],"summary":"CSS 函数 matrix() 指定了一个由指定的 6 个值组成的 2D 变换矩阵。这种矩阵的常量值是隐含的，而不是由参数传递的；其他的参数是以列优先的顺序描述的。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"matrix()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"matrix()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"matrix()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"matrix()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"matrix()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"matrix()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/css/transform-function/matrix","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/css/transform-function/matrix/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS（层叠样式表）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transform-function","title":"transform-function"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transform-function/matrix","title":"matrix()"}],"pageTitle":"matrix() - CSS（层叠样式表） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}